Package: droughtwatch
Title: Agricultural Drought Monitoring and Early Warning System
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sohaib", "Jabrane", email = "sohaib.jabrane@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for monitoring agricultural drought
    and generating early warning alerts. It provides tools to calculate 
    standard drought indices (SPI, SPEI, VHI), analyze NDVI vegetation data,
    detect drought episodes, produce risk maps, and generate automated 
    monthly bulletins and interactive dashboards.
